{"word":"μητιάω","slug":"μητιάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μητιάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μῆτις'><el>μῆτις</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to meditate, deliberate, debate</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>μητιάασθε</el> <i>consider among you</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, = <a href='S:μητίομαι'><el>μητίομαι</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}